main event: A witness observed a bright, large, silent object floating and gliding rapidly across the sky at tree-top level in Vineland, New Jersey.
interesting points: The object did not have any running lights and made no sound.
The witness watched the object for over a minute as it glided across the sky and then seemed to disappear into the clouds.
The witness was quite upset by the sighting, as they had never seen anything like it before.
The sighting occurred during a rainy and thunderstorming night while the witness was driving.
The witness is willing to cooperate further if more information is needed.
sighted object: a bright, large, silent object floating and gliding rapidly across the sky
